# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Dependencies
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
node_modules/
**/node_modules

# Benchmark/eval fixture-seed lockfiles are install artifacts (their package.json +
# node_modules are ignored too); keep them untracked so dependabot does not scan
# stale fixture deps. Real MCP-server lockfiles elsewhere stay tracked + scanned.
**/seed/package-lock.json

